Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:19.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:25.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,A thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:31.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:37.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:43.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:49.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:58.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\NAs the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:06.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:12.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:18.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:24.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:44.36,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, who had been aboard the Cat's\NEye on a recon mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:48.63,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,was taken prisoner along with her escorts\NHikaru, Max, and Kakizaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:52.92,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and transported far away to\Nthe main Zentradi fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:57.20,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The scale and power of the enemy fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:02:00.79,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the physical strength\Nof the Zentradi themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:04.02,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,was beyond anything they\Ncould have imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:18.53,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(88,119)}BIG ESCAPE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:15.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:16.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:18.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one thing to say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:24.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At that meeting earlier, the giants were\Nshocked when the Lieutenant and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:26.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When they had us kiss, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:28.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And they said something about "Protoculture."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:33.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they were so freaked out they\Ndidn't even move for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:38.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we wait until the next time a soldier comes\Nin to feed us and then kiss again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:42.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotcha! When the soldier gets all\Nsurprised, we escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking!\NI won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:45.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:48.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your big plan?\NUnbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that would work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:54.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'd actually kiss you again\Nbased on a half-baked plan like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:57.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NDo you have any other choices?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:01.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if it wasn't to get out of here, why\Nwould I wanna kiss someone like you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:01.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:04.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:09.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Hayase, this time I'd be glad to\Ntrade places with Lt. Ichijo, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:12.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What a moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:27.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Bodolzaa, what strategy did you\Nhave in mind for further operations?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to send in a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:30.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:36.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pardon, sir, but contact with the\NProtoculture could lead to our destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:37.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:42.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}But if we can get our hands on their reaction\Nweaponry or shipboard repair technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see those miclone civilians again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:45.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}We would gain a great advantage\Nover the Supervision Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:43.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:45.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:48.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But who could endure a mission requiring\Nthem to become miclones
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and infiltrate this most\Nunusual "Macross" ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:55.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please allow us to carry out this mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:03:57.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You three?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:58.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:04.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... Maybe we should try\Nyour plan after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:11.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This video could change the\Ncourse of human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:14.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my duty as a soldier to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:16.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:19.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Lt. Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Duty, Duty!"\NWhy, it's so honorable of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:23.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're a soldier too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now are you going to do this or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who suggested it, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's earlier than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakizaki, get ready by the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:33.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:46.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:47.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:55.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:57.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck were you guys trying to do, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later.\NLet's get out of here, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:01.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:05.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hop on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:08.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:10.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakizaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You go over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Three's a crowd, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really count on those three?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just to get a glimpse\Nof the inside of that ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:25.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,then they should be up to the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:29.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been completely unable to comprehend\Nthe miclones' activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm pretty surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure that other girl was your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea you were into older women.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:39.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!\NIt was just part of our plan to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:46.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. If we make it back to the\NMacross, I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:48.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it at all!\NYou've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you yell, they'll be sure to find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:13.27,Zent,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Muetema!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:16.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:18.74,Zent,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Adoua!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about the bumpy ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Britai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:43.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The prisoners have escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Accursed miclones!\NWhat are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture them, no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:11.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, sir.\NIt won't move at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.\NWhat should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to make a break for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:34.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:35.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think Max and Kakizaki are all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:11.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:18.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The giants...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The giants are getting smaller!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:55.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't caught them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:58.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir. I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that they're so small...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:01.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Britai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:02.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you need to take responsibility\Nfor this blunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:10.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you off the front line for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:14.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And what of the plan to send in our spies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have Lap'Lamiz handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:19.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lap'Lamiz of the Direct-Defense Fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:23.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NThat's how important this operation is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what the giants meant\Nby "miclone," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:33.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotten our hands on some\Nimportant information.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Ichijo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:41.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a thought, but maybe these giants\Nwere originally the same size as we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, to fight this enemy they call\Nthe "Supervision Army,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:49.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,they could have rebuilt their own bodies\Ninto something bigger and stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:51.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:55.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a humanoid that can\Nsurvive the vacuum of space
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:10:00.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight a Battroid barehanded could\Nhave been born naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they did some kind of\Ngenetic engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:08.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If they have the technology to\Ngo from giant to miclone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,it wouldn't be a stretch to imagine\Nthey could do the reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:12.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:15.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:20.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this "Protoculture" they mentioned\Nwas the civilization they had
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,when they were still our size.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:05.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:09.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:12.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Ichijo, it's all over.\NJust leave me and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:14.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Without the data, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in saving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:20.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:25.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without the data, we witnessed\Nit all ourselves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:28.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All the more reason for you to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:31.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking!\NThere's no way I could abandon a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.48,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Goodbye, Hikaru. Goodbye!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:08.96,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}"Where are you going? Minmay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.32,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Minmay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally come around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Hayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like cooling water for\Ntheir engines or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooling water?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:31.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty bad, huh? They don't seem to\Nmaintain their ships very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that fact saved our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:38.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And since I didn't drown, I guess\Nthat means I owe you one, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:41.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could abandon a\Ncomrade-in-arms, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.19,0:12:43.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's that.\NNow we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:55.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the giants have such a huge fleet\Nbut not even maintain their ships properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:57.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they want to, but they can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:59.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:06.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, turning themselves into giants definitely\Nmade them optimally suited to be soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:11.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe they lost\Nsomething in the process too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:12.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:16.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, and proof of that is that\Nthere are no civilians,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and there's no interaction between\Nmen and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:22.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So getting their bodies that powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,made them unable to think of\Nanything but fighting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:33.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"The universe overflows with conflict, and\Nit is in battle that one finds life."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:38.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When two fleets as big as this duke it out,\Nit must be incredible, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:41.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling how many worlds\Nhave been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:43.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:47.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet people the same size as us would have\Nbeen destroyed in an instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:50.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and when they were, all kinds\Nof cultures were lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:55.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And those lost cultures...\Nthat's Protoculture?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.41,0:13:58.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's why the giants are so\Ninterested in us and the Macross,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:02.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,because we have Protoculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:06.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it, it's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans who only think about fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,True. They're just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:18.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,For over a hundred years, my family\Nhas served in the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:22.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was in grade school,\Nall I've wanted to be was a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,My head was filled with ideas of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You were top of your class at\Nthe academy, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:29.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're famous among the pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:34.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They say, "Lt. Top-of-Her-Class is\Nscarier than a demon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:35.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:42.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,See, that's why Claudia teases me whenever\NI even try to talk about men.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:47.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lt. Hayase, you were at the top of\Nyour class! I'm shocked!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:52.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love with someone back\Non the Macross, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:54.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:59.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You were talking in your sleep.\N"Minmay! Minmay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.23,0:15:01.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:02.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's your girlfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:09.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But since she became Miss Macross\Nand decided to be a singer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:13.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we haven't really had much time\Nto see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's going to be a singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:17.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think she's already had\Nher debut by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably a big idol\Non the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's great, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:26.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Having someone you love makes you want to\Nget back to the Macross, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The only boyfriend I have is my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:32.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get back, you'll find\Nsomeone for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you acted more like the way\Nyou are now, like a lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of your elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:48.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's just another reason we\Nhave to get back to the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:51.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:52.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:16:00.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Loli Dosel and two other class-one\Narmored troops, reporting for duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:05.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you volunteered to\Nbecome miclone spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:06.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was our honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:10.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Infiltrate the enemy ship and obtain\Ndetailed intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:14.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When you return, you'll be given\Nyour own armored corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:21.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Board your vessel, the Bekamli 220,\Nand make for the enemy ship at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:21.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:26.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:28.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:35.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.17,0:16:50.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, that's an incredible fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:54.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we wouldn't stand a chance\Neven if we put up a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow we have to put an\Nend to the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:01.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, we have to think about how\Nwe're going to get back to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:12.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max!\NKakizaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:14.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:16.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That ship looks like it's about\Nto leave, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:23.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:28.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're loading supplies from\Nthe ship we came in on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe we can get back to Earth.\NTo the Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're gonna do that,\Nwe'd better sneak aboard fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sneaking spies aboard the enemy ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A rather passive plan, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:19.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your tongue, Milia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:21.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But Commander Lap'Lamiz...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:25.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,These are special orders from his Lordship,\NSupreme Commander Bodolzaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:31.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This enemy could be even more dangerous\Nthan the Supervision Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:34.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships commencing fold navigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:43.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How do we get out of here once they de-fold?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:47.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, how about stealing one\Nof those battle pods?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And how do you intend to pilot the thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:52.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! I mean, we do have\Nthree splendid pilots right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:53.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you don't want to get back\Nto the Macross after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:57.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, about getting those spies\Naboard the enemy ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:09.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just miclones. I can more\Nthan handle them by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:11.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I expected to hear,\NMilia. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:16.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're de-folding!\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:18.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If these things were easy to pilot,\Nwe wouldn't be having this problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:26.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you three will ride in this capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:27.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told that Milia of the\NLap'Lamiz Direct-Defense Fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,will be delivering you to the enemy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:34.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Milia?\NYou mean Milia the Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:36.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, so you can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:41.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Queadluun is ready for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll draw the enemy ship's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:22.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to see those "civilians" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:26.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:30.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We de-folded ages ago!\NGet a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:33.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's scarier than a demon, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:34.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just talking in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:36.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:42.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course they did.\NMax!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:44.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! That's got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:02.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a battle's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope this is our solar system.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:11.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:12.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the comm unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:14.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:20.59,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:19.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Minmay's song!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.81,0:21:20.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:25.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:22.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means... Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:25.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!\NThe Macross is out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:28.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shining, making a rapid descent
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:32.40,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then BOOM! he makes a sudden climb
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:38.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leaving a long trail of vapor
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:44.40,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He traces two big hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:42.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the enemy that's more dangerous\Nthan the Supervision Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:43.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,These beings aren't worth my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:51.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A love sign in the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:51.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:55.29,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I love you, you love me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:59.64,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he's head over heels
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:06.05,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For his plane instead of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.39,0:22:09.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:10.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:16.52,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:23.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Flight Commander Milia to\NCommander Lap'Lamiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:25.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete.\NI am returning to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.37,0:22:28.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.\NWell done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:31.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now withdraw from the front line.\NHead for the rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:37.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant! I've locked onto\Nour military frequency!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.47,0:22:40.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really going to be rescued, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.49,0:22:42.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we make contact before we\Nget shot down by our own people?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:45.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!\NPlease come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.39,0:22:49.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Macross Bridge Operator\NMisa Hayase and three others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:52.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have stolen an enemy pod\Nand are currently adrift!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:54.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Requesting assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:35.42,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(81,107)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:35.42,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,453)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:38.80,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth was finally right before the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:43.58,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The important information Hikaru\Nand the others brought back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.91,0:23:47.85,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,made Captain Global only more determined\Nto break through the enemy blockade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.50,0:23:54.15,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, by this time, Zentradi spies\Nhad already infiltrated the Macross.
